{"name": "Concussive Force", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/air/wind-vortex-swirl-blue-purple.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A ball of condensed air appears in your hand as you reel back your arm and throw it at a point within range that you can see.  Every creature within a 20 foot radius sphere originating from that point must make a Strength (Save) check.  On failure, they take 10d6 force damage, and are knocked @Compendium[undertaking.conditions.RK3DF56CKMQUV6DM]{Prone}.  On success, they take half as much damage and are not knocked @Compendium[undertaking.conditions.RK3DF56CKMQUV6DM]{Prone}.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": false, "school": "evo", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": true, "ritual": false, "concentration": false}, "materials": {"value": "a small jade bead", "consumed": false, "cost": "", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "save", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "inst"}, "range": {"value": "120", "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "target": {"value": "20", "width": null, "units": "ft", "type": "sphere"}, "damage": {"parts": [["10d6", "force"]], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "str", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "NOK5D400Y0BRTL1N", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Grave Ring", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/unholy/barrier-fire-pink.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A ring of black flames appears and spins out into a 60 foot radius sphere from a point of your choosing that is within range that you can see.  All creatures caught in the area must make a Constitution (Save) check.  On a failed save the target takes 8d6 necrotic damage, or half as much on a successful save.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": false, "school": "nec", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": true, "ritual": false, "concentration": false}, "materials": {"value": "powder from a crushed black gemstone worth at least 500 gp", "consumed": false, "cost": "500", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "save", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "inst"}, "range": {"value": "150", "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "target": {"value": "60", "width": null, "units": "ft", "type": "sphere"}, "damage": {"parts": [["8d6", "necrotic"]], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "con", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "5QKNDIU0N7AOHVQT", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Hundred Spear Assault", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/skills/melee/spear-tips-quintuple-orange.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>At your call, a hundred ghostly spears are volleyed forward and fall in a line that is 100 feet long and 10 feet wide in a direction that you choose.  Creatures caught in the line must make a Dexterity (Save) check.  On failure, they take 7d6 piercing damage and 4d6 force damage, and have their speed reduced to 0 feet until the end of their next turn as the piercing spears hold targets in place.  On success, they take half damage and do not have their speed reduced.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": false, "school": "evo", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": true, "ritual": false, "concentration": false}, "materials": {"value": "miniature spear totem", "consumed": false, "cost": "", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "save", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "inst"}, "range": {"value": "0", "long": null, "units": "self"}, "target": {"value": "100", "width": null, "units": "ft", "type": "line"}, "damage": {"parts": [["7d6", "piercing"], ["4d6", "force"]], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "dex", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "3I736YDSAFN1B3E3", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Null Field", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-pink.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A shimmering field appears as an immobile barrier that forms in a 10 foot radius centered around you and remains for the duration.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Any spell that is of 5th level or lower cast from outside the barrier has no effect on creatures and objects within it, even if the spell is Charged to have a more powerful effect.  Such spells can target creatures and objects within the barrier, but the spell will have no effect on them.  As well, the area within the barrier is excluded from the areas of affect from spells of these levels.<br><br>Charge: This spell can be Charged to provide better protection:<ul><li>2 Mana: Spells of up to 6th level cannot penetrate the barrier.</li></ul></p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": true, "school": "abj", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": true, "ritual": false, "concentration": true}, "materials": {"value": "an engraved crystal bead that shatters when the spell ends", "consumed": true, "cost": "", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "util", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "1", "units": "minute"}, "range": {"value": "0", "long": null, "units": "self"}, "target": {"value": "10", "width": null, "units": "ft", "type": "sphere"}, "damage": {"parts": [], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "J3C64S01EREH1FZZ", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Restore", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-green.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A creature that you can see within range is overwhelmed by restorative energy.  This creature regains 70 hit points, and is cured of @Compendium[undertaking.conditions.ADW4EH0NKRDCRCA4]{Blindness}, @Compendium[undertaking.conditions.WK17M9FZR08DRUP1]{Deafness}, and any @Compendium[undertaking.conditions.9YPWLY1IHQV3MRLO]{Disease} affecting it.  This spell has no effect on constructs or undead.  <br><br>Charge: This spell can be charged to provide better protection:<ul><li>2 Mana: The creature recovers 10 more hit points.</li></ul></p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": true, "school": "evo", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": false, "ritual": false, "concentration": false}, "materials": {"value": "", "consumed": false, "cost": "", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "heal", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "inst"}, "range": {"value": "60", "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "target": {"value": "1", "width": null, "units": "", "type": "creature"}, "damage": {"parts": [["70", "healing"]], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "5RC7X7J6H9UK5K29", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Ruin", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/death/hand-withered-gray.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You magically unleash a vicious disease on the immune system of a creature that you can see within range.  The target must make a Constitution (Save) check.  On failure, it takes 14d6 necrotic damage and contracts Ruin Disease.  On success, the target takes half damage and is not @Compendium[undertaking.conditions.9YPWLY1IHQV3MRLO]{Diseased}.  The damage cannot reduce the target\u2019s hit points below 1.  <br><br><i>Ruin Disease:</i> The target\u2019s hit point maximum is reduced by the same amount as the damage dealt when contracted to a minimum of 1 hit point, and remains this way until cured or until 1 hour passes.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": false, "school": "nec", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": false, "ritual": false, "concentration": false}, "materials": {"value": "", "consumed": false, "cost": "", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "save", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "inst"}, "range": {"value": "60", "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "target": {"value": "1", "width": null, "units": "", "type": "creature"}, "damage": {"parts": [["14d6", "necrotic"]], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "con", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "GAC3VH4EZJOKZ8U0", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Sonic Shatter Spike", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/sonic/explosion-shock-wave-teal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A large crystalline shard of aether materializes before you and rushes towards a target that you choose that you can see within range.  Roll a ranged spell attack.  On hit, the target takes 6d10 piercing damage.  In either case the shard explodes, causing all creatures within 10 feet of the initial target to make a Dexterity (Save) check.  On failure, that creature takes 4d6 piercing damage, or half as much on a success. <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;At the beginning of your next turn all creatures injured or affected by this spell must make a Constitution (Save) check as the crystalline shards that hit them shatter in a sonic blast.  On a failure, a target takes 5d6 force damage, but takes half as much damage on a success.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "level": "6", "charge": false, "school": "evo", "components": {"somatic": true, "verbal": true, "material": false, "ritual": false, "concentration": false}, "materials": {"value": "", "consumed": false, "cost": "", "supply": 0}, "attribute": "spell", "actionType": "rsak", "activation": {"type": "action", "cost": "1", "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "inst"}, "range": {"value": "60", "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "target": {"value": "10", "width": null, "units": "ft", "type": "sphere"}, "damage": {"parts": [["6d10", "piercing"], ["4d6", "piercing"], ["5d6", "force"]], "versatile": ""}, "save": {"attribute": "dex", "dc": null, "scaling": "spell"}, "showInAttacks": false}, "_id": "8HOLU9HRLA5TTMWE", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
